wuz ^? i am sooooo bored. well, i wen to a garage sale with my aunt and my mom today. it was all around boring. except for the part where her hot nephew came over for a few minutes. he's 14 or 15 and i'm 13. omg!!! and i was supposed to spend the night when he was but we both couldn't. i don't think he knew i was going to but o well. i think i'm going back over there tomorrow but i'm not sure. i get to call my friends tomorrow to see if they can spend the night. they all had plans during the weekend so i was all alone. i was in a car accident last weekend on this very night. i went to preroll newspapers with my dad for extra money and we were at an intersection when this DEAF CHINEESE HANDICAP pulls in front of us and hits the passenger side of our truck. i used to make fun of the truck because i thought it was ugly but it saved my life. i am so thankfull to God everytime something good happens in my life. it really makes me mad when people doubt his miracles. i mean, there have been so many instances when i need Him and He helped me. one time i remember: my dog BUBBA was really sick and i was sooo scared. my dad said that if he didn't get better that they were going to have to put him to sleep because we didn't have the money for him to get helped. well, he was laying on the couch and i went in there and hugged him for a long time crying. i prayed that he would be healed and that he wouldn't die. i promised that i would always take care of him and let him in my room. at the time i had a canopy in my room so that was a big deal. but, the next day he was doing so much better. i mean, he was aweful for a while, he couldn't move and he wouldn't eat or drink anything. he was really active and had alot of energy when we first got him but then when he was sick we knew there was only one person who could help us. or at least i knew...God. well, i'm getting pretty tired of typing so i'll be on later!
